      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "I remember this one time\u2026 ohh yes\u2026 a lovely lass came
          to town. Crying, she was\u2026 tears all down her cheeks\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977024
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "Said her husband had cheated on her. Cheated! Can you imagine\u2026
          the nerve\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977025
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "And the girl.. She was so pretty\u2026 such a shame\u2026 I simply
          had to help her\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977026
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "Now lucky for her\u2026 very lucky, in fact\u2014it was the holy
          year! Yes! A holy year for the church\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977027
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "Which meant! That if her husband only made the pilgrimage\u2026
          all the way to the holy door of Saint Peter\u2019s Basilica\u2026 in the
          Vatican\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977028
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: Then God would forgive him of all his sins!
    - rid: 8780718627794977029
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: All of them! Just like that! Clean slate! Fresh start!
    - rid: 8780718627794977030
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "\u2026Convenient, isn\u2019t it?"
    - rid: 8780718627794977031
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "And then they could be together again\u2026 no more dirty baggage\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977032
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "Heh\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977033
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "\u2026Of course\u2026 I don\u2019t know if he ever went\u2026"
    - rid: 8780718627794977034
      type: {class: 'Constant`1[[System.String, mscorlib]]', ns: Unity.GraphToolkit.Editor, asm: Unity.GraphToolkit.Internal.Editor}
      data:
        m_Value: "Or if she ever stopped crying\u2026"
